streams.work_experience_description:
Have been working in regional Queensland for at least the last 3 months.
After you obtained your qualification
Closely related to your nominated occupation
At least 30 hours per week
When you submit your EOI for Queensland nomination, you must still be employed in a role that meets the above requirements.

Have evidence that your employment is ongoing for a further 6 months. This is counted from when you submit your EOI.
streams.other_requirement: Must commit to living and working in Queensland for 2 years from date your visa is granted.
